reviewText:
The print was bad and parts of the movie were deleted.

Some parts were okay as far as the print was concerned however, most parts were not.

this is a hilarious movie. although quite old so some of the sound effects are off, you'll still enjoy this one. I first watched this growing up as a child, and have been looking all over for this movie, as i have good memories of it on vhs. thanks amazon for stocking this movie!!
